name: What you think you become
description:
Shot with lovely Olympus Pen FT on Kodak Gold 200, developed in Gelin Lab and scanned with Plustek OpticFilm 8200i.
Lonhhua temple is the largest and most authentic Buddhist temple in Shanghai. Its history dates back to 242 AD. It has been rebuilt few times later on. This is the central statue of three bodies of Buddha (Trikaya).
